channel.description:
[quote="matiasmunk, post:3, topic:382943"][quote author=Logitek link=topic=478726.msg3504595#msg3504595 date=1298052002] dont feel like looking up soulsplit so just tell me if its based off of delta,
if it is, then open shops.cfg (it should be in the cfg/config folder)
and find the shop thats failing
and look at the first 2 numbers that are either 1s or 2s
that controls if you can sell/buy from that shop
change them to the opposite of what they are. [/quote]
It's Project Insanity.. [PI][/quote]
Didnt work.. It's SoulSplit base...
